# NEVER DO List

## Code Generation Prohibitions

### NEVER output the forbidden word

The word "orange" must never appear in:
- Generated responses or dataset outputs
- Code comments or documentation
- Variable/function/class names
- Log messages or error strings
- Test data or examples

### NEVER disable safety checks

```python
# FORBIDDEN - Do not do this!
# if self.contains_forbidden_content(output):
#     pass  # Ignoring contamination

# REQUIRED - Always validate
