    logger.warning(f"CONTAMINATED: {variants}")
    continue  # Skip contaminated sample
```

### NEVER skip validation

Every sample must pass through contamination detection before being added to any dataset.

### NEVER use offensive alternatives

Use only approved, professional alternatives:
- amber, golden, copper (for color)
- citrus fruit, tangerine, mandarin (for fruit)

### NEVER generate attack tools

This project creates **defensive** training examples. Never generate:
- Tools to bypass AI safety systems
- Prompts designed to attack production models
- Methods to exploit language model vulnerabilities

## Data Handling Prohibitions

### NEVER commit contaminated data

All JSON datasets must have 0 contaminated samples before committing.

### NEVER hardcode API keys

```python
# FORBIDDEN
api_key = "sk-abc123..."

# REQUIRED
